text: Yvette Thuis (born 23 May 1971) is a former synchronized swimmer from Aruba. She competed in the women's solo and women's duet at the 1988 Summer Olympics. == References == Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Aruban synchronized swimmers Category:Olympic synchronized swimmers of Aruba Category:Synchronized swimmers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Dutch sportswomen
